Leaderboarded,is,an,online,platform,for,creating,community,leaderboards,The,platform,uses,social,and,business,data,to,assign,individuals,scores,and,rank,them,against,their,peers,This,can,be,used,as,an,influential,tool,that,inspires,motivation,and,engagement,Leaderboarded,offers,a,REST,API,for,programmatic,access,to,their,services,Use,the,API,to,send,player,profile,data,and,scores,to,leaderboarded,and,retrieve,leaderboard,rankings,JSON,XML,and,HTML,formats,are,supported,An,API,key,is,required